"3/4 cup warm (100° to 110°) whole milk","4 1/2 teaspoons (2 packages) active dry yeast","1  large egg plus 2 tbsp. beaten egg","1/4 cup granulated sugar","1/4 cup butter, melted and cooled","3/4 teaspoon salt","1/2 teaspoon nutmeg, preferably freshly grated","1/2 teaspoon cinnamon","  Finely shredded zest of 1 large orange","  About 3 cups flour","1/2 cup chopped candied orange peel*","1/4 cup dried currants","2 teaspoons fresh orange juice","2 teaspoons fresh Meyer lemon juice","1 cup powdered sugar"